org.apache.ambari.server.ldap.domain

Class AmbariLdapConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.configuration.AmbariServerConfiguration
      • org.apache.ambari.server.ldap.domain.AmbariLdapConfiguration

  • public class AmbariLdapConfiguration
extends AmbariServerConfiguration
    This class is a representation of all the LDAP related configuration properties.

    IMPORTANT: in case you declare any new LDAP related property please do it in the Python class stacks.ambari_configuration.AmbariLDAPConfiguration too.
